{"id":722527628,"question_id":583,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 12 months","timestamp":1655261688,"status":14,"status_display":"Time Limit Exceeded","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/722527628/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Delete Operation for Two Strings","memory":"N/A","code":"public class Solution {\n    public int minDistance(String s1, String s2) {\n        return s1.length() + s2.length() - 2 * lcs(s1, s2, s1.length(), s2.length());\n    }\n    public int lcs(String s1, String s2, int m, int n) {\n        if (m == 0 || n == 0)\n            return 0;\n        if (s1.charAt(m - 1) == s2.charAt(n - 1))\n            return 1 + lcs(s1, s2, m - 1, n - 1);\n        else\n            return Math.max(lcs(s1, s2, m, n - 1), lcs(s1, s2, m - 1, n));\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"delete-operation-for-two-strings","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
